Thorsten ANDERSON, Appellant, v. A. E. BURNETT, District Director, U. S. Immigration Service, etc., Appellee. No. 7308. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. Oct. 16, 1933. John Beardsley, of Los Angeles, Cal., for appellant. Peirson M. Hall, U. S. Atty., of Los Angeles, Cal., for appellee.

Before WILBUR, SAWTELLE, and GARRECHT, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Upon stipulation of counsel for respective parties, ordered appeal in this cause dismissed; mandate forthwith..
